description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Yoga Full Body Stretches for Tension and Sore Muscles' from the channel Yoga With Bird.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a 15 min yoga full body stretch for tension and sore muscle relief. This quick yoga class stretches the entire body to help you feel your best mentally and physically anytime of the day. Use these stretches in the morning or evening!
